        <Summary>MariaDB which is its binary version published by mariadb team is a drop-in replacement for MySQL.</Summary>
        <Description>It is binary code which compiled by MariaDB and relases from https://downloads.mariadb.org/mariadb/10.4.8/. MariaDB strives to be the logical choice for database professionals looking for a robust, scalable, and reliable SQL server.</Description>
